Quickstrike:





Quickstrike turned his head and glowered at Dark Mouse. "Ah wasn't 
scared. Ya jus' caught me of guard, is all."

He had too much pride.

He looked past Paraylsis and waved him off. He opened his comm-link 
and said: "Hey, sugar-bot ah'm here. Now somethin' ya want me t' do 
fer ya?"
